[2026-07-07T04:39:20.697Z] [INFO] [stderr]  ## 1. What It Is
[2026-07-07T04:39:20.697Z] [INFO] [stderr]  
[2026-07-07T04:39:20.697Z] [INFO] [stderr]  - **Local-first**: All data lives in your browser. You own it.
[2026-07-07T04:39:20.697Z] [INFO] [stderr]  ### Core Philosophy
[2026-07-07T04:39:20.697Z] [INFO] [stderr] [0m
[2026-07-07T04:39:20.697Z] [INFO] [stderr] +IELTS Learning Journey is a comprehensive study tool for IELTS exam preparation. It helps learners manage vocabulary, practice all four IELTS skills (Reading, Listening, Writing, Speaking), track mistakes, monitor progress, and optionally use AI for feedback — all while keeping data private and local. The codebase is also designed to be AI coding agent-friendly, enabling automated code exploration and safe, predictable modifications.
